INDICATOR_NAME: Unemployment, youth male (% of male labor force ages 15-24) (national estimate)
SOURCE_NOTE: Youth unemployment refers to the share of the labor force ages 15-24 without work but available for and seeking employment. Definitions of labor force and unemployment differ by country.
SOURCE_ORGANIZATION: Labour Force Statistics database (LFS), International Labour Organization (ILO), uri: https://ilostat.ilo.org/data/bulk/, publisher: ILOSTAT, type: external database, date accessed: September 25, 2025
